{"id":26,"date":"2023-09-18T22:22:12","date_gmt":"2023-09-18T22:22:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/?page_id=26"},"modified":"2024-11-08T17:03:33","modified_gmt":"2024-11-08T17:03:33","slug":"facilities","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/facilities\/","title":{"rendered":"Facilities"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Experimental settings<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\">Our experimental devices are arranged to render 3D objects that appear to be floating in space beyond the mirror. Participants look into a half-silvered mirror slanted at 45\u00b0 relative to the sagittal body midline, and the mirror reflects the image displayed on a 19&#8243; CRT monitor placed directly to the left of the mirror. Stereoscopic presentation is achieved with a frame interlacing technique in conjunction with liquid-crystal goggles synchronized to the frame rate. To provide consistent vergence and accommodative information, the monitor is mounted on a linear positioning stage that can be situated on each trial to match the rendered viewing distance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"341\" src=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-52\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_-300x100.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_-768x256.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_3-1024x485.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-55\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_3-1024x485.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_3-300x142.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_3-768x364.jpg 768w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_3-1536x727.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_3.jpg 1905w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:111px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Renderings of 3D objects<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Participants view stereoscopic renderings of 3D objects in a tabletop virtual reality setup, and either judge or interact with the virtual objects.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" src=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3893.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-520\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3893.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3893-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3893-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3893-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3893-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3893-200x133.jpg 200w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3893-660x440.jpg 660w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1281\" src=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3669-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-584\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3669-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3669-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3669-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3669-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3669-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3669-1-200x133.jpg 200w, https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2024\/11\/CoPsy-3DIPA-Lab_673A3669-1-660x440.jpg 660w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:111px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Motion tracking and haptic devices<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The linear positioning stages and stepper motors align physical objects with the virtual stimulus, which allows participants to interact with the objects and receive haptic feedback. Movements are tracked by using an Optotrak Certus motion-capture system, which is coupled to our tabletop virtual reality environment. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video crossorigin=\"anonymous\" height=\"683\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 1024 \/ 683;\" width=\"1024\" autoplay loop muted src=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/files\/2023\/09\/facil_1.webm\" playsinline><\/video><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Experimental settings Our experimental devices are arranged to render 3D objects that appear to be floating in space beyond the&hellip; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/facilities\/\">Read more <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Facilities<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2180,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-26","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/26","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2180"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26"}],"version-history":[{"count":16,"href":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/26\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":673,"href":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/26\/revisions\/673"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sites.brown.edu\/3dipalab\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=26"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}